{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I grew up in a very small country town"},{"time":2463,"text":"in Victoria."},{"time":3763,"text":"I had a very normal, low-key kind of upbringing."},{"time":8180,"text":"I went to school, I hung out with my friends,"},{"time":11580,"text":"I fought with my younger sisters."},{"time":13966,"text":"It was all very normal."},{"time":15755,"text":"And when I was 15, a member of my local community"},{"time":19927,"text":"approached my parents"},{"time":21347,"text":"and wanted to nominate me"},{"time":22740,"text":"for a community achievement award."},{"time":25860,"text":"And my parents said, \"Hm, that's really nice,"},{"time":29103,"text":"but there's kind of one glaring problem with that."},{"time":32320,"text":"She hasn't actually achieved anything.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":37254,"text":"And they were right, you know."},{"time":38849,"text":"I went to school, I got good marks,"},{"time":41835,"text":"I had a very low-key after school job"},{"time":44283,"text":"in my mum's hairdressing salon,"},{"time":46065,"text":"and I spent a lot of time watching"},{"time":47863,"text":"\"Buffy the Vampire Slayer\" and \"Dawson's Creek.\""},{"time":50994,"text":"Yeah, I know. What a contradiction."},{"time":55037,"text":"But they were right, you know."},{"time":56377,"text":"I wasn't doing anything that was out of the ordinary"},{"time":58930,"text":"at all."},{"time":60611,"text":"I wasn't doing anything that could\nbe considered an achievement"},{"time":63554,"text":"if you took disability out of the equation."},{"time":67156,"text":"Years later, I was on my second teaching round"},{"time":71022,"text":"in a Melbourne high school,"},{"time":72758,"text":"and I was about 20 minutes into\na year 11 legal studies class"},{"time":77709,"text":"when this boy put up his hand and said,"},{"time":79488,"text":"\"Hey miss, when are you going\nto start doing your speech?\""},{"time":83732,"text":"And I said, \"What speech?\""},{"time":85709,"text":"You know, I'd been talking them"},{"time":87013,"text":"about defamation law for a good 20 minutes."},{"time":89909,"text":"And he said, \"You know, like,"},{"time":91580,"text":"your motivational speaking."},{"time":93900,"text":"You know, when people in\nwheelchairs come to school,"},{"time":95890,"text":"they usually say, like, inspirational stuff?\""},{"time":100813,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":102259,"text":"\"It's usually in the big hall.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":106557,"text":"And that's when it dawned on me:"},{"time":108770,"text":"This kid had only ever experienced disabled people"},{"time":112041,"text":"as objects of inspiration."},{"time":115699,"text":"We are not, to this kid --"},{"time":117560,"text":"and it's not his fault, I mean,"},{"time":118861,"text":"that's true for many of us."},{"time":120672,"text":"For lots of us, disabled people are not our teachers"},{"time":124418,"text":"or our doctors or our manicurists."},{"time":127477,"text":"We're not real people. We are there to inspire."},{"time":132846,"text":"And in fact, I am sitting on this stage"},{"time":136352,"text":"looking like I do in this wheelchair,"},{"time":139434,"text":"and you are probably kind of expecting me"},{"time":142367,"text":"to inspire you. Right? (Laughter)"},{"time":147147,"text":"Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149990,"text":"Well, ladies and gentlemen, I'm afraid"},{"time":152004,"text":"I'm going to disappoint you dramatically."},{"time":154861,"text":"I am not here to inspire you."},{"time":157030,"text":"I am here to tell you that we have been lied to"},{"time":159607,"text":"about disability."},{"time":161574,"text":"Yeah, we've been sold the lie"},{"time":163681,"text":"that disability is a Bad Thing, capital B, capital T."},{"time":168886,"text":"It's a bad thing, and to live with a disability"},{"time":171827,"text":"makes you exceptional."},{"time":173973,"text":"It's not a bad thing, and it doesn't"},{"time":176888,"text":"make you exceptional."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179517,"text":"And in the past few years, we've been able"},{"time":181252,"text":"to propagate this lie even further"},{"time":183875,"text":"via social media."},{"time":186149,"text":"You may have seen images like this one:"},{"time":188382,"text":"\"The only disability in life is a bad attitude.\""},{"time":192975,"text":"Or this one: \"Your excuse is invalid.\" Indeed."},{"time":197326,"text":"Or this one: \"Before you quit, try!\""},{"time":203686,"text":"These are just a couple of examples,"},{"time":205342,"text":"but there are a lot of these images out there."},{"time":207311,"text":"You know, you might have seen the one,"},{"time":208940,"text":"the little girl with no hands"},{"time":210689,"text":"drawing a picture with a pencil held in her mouth."},{"time":214400,"text":"You might have seen a child running"},{"time":216120,"text":"on carbon fiber prosthetic legs."},{"time":218993,"text":"And these images,"},{"time":220344,"text":"there are lots of them out there,"},{"time":221970,"text":"they are what we call inspiration porn."},{"time":225884,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":228110,"text":"And I use the term porn deliberately,"},{"time":230328,"text":"because they objectify one group of people"},{"time":233477,"text":"for the benefit of another group of people."},{"time":236288,"text":"So in this case, we're objectifying disabled people"},{"time":239167,"text":"for the benefit of nondisabled people."},{"time":241824,"text":"The purpose of these images"},{"time":243952,"text":"is to inspire you, to motivate you,"},{"time":247763,"text":"so that we can look at them"},{"time":249838,"text":"and think, \"Well, however bad my life is,"},{"time":252927,"text":"it could be worse."},{"time":254958,"text":"I could be that person.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":258286,"text":"But what if you are that person?"},{"time":261662,"text":"I've lost count of the number of times that I've"},{"time":263750,"text":"been approached by strangers"},{"time":266218,"text":"wanting to tell me that they think I'm brave"},{"time":269123,"text":"or inspirational,"},{"time":270880,"text":"and this was long before my work"},{"time":272539,"text":"had any kind of public profile."},{"time":274593,"text":"They were just kind of congratulating me"},{"time":276295,"text":"for managing to get up in the morning"},{"time":278001,"text":"and remember my own name. (Laughter)"},{"time":282009,"text":"And it is objectifying."},{"time":284547,"text":"These images, those images"},{"time":286640,"text":"objectify disabled people"},{"time":288571,"text":"for the benefit of nondisabled people."},{"time":291496,"text":"They are there so that you can look at them"},{"time":294110,"text":"and think that things aren't so bad for you,"},{"time":296813,"text":"to put your worries into perspective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300960,"text":"And life as a disabled person"},{"time":303881,"text":"is actually somewhat difficult."},{"time":305965,"text":"We do overcome some things."},{"time":308071,"text":"But the things that we're overcoming"},{"time":310283,"text":"are not the things that you think they are."},{"time":312900,"text":"They are not things to do with our bodies."},{"time":315507,"text":"I use the term \"disabled people\" quite deliberately,"},{"time":317885,"text":"because I subscribe to what's called\nthe social model of disability,"},{"time":322083,"text":"which tells us that we are more disabled"},{"time":324381,"text":"by the society that we live in"},{"time":328295,"text":"than by our bodies and our diagnoses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331178,"text":"So I have lived in this body a long time."},{"time":335086,"text":"I'm quite fond of it."},{"time":337349,"text":"It does the things that I need it to do,"},{"time":340402,"text":"and I've learned to use it to the best of its capacity"},{"time":343695,"text":"just as you have,"},{"time":344829,"text":"and that's the thing about those\nkids in those pictures as well."},{"time":347853,"text":"They're not doing anything out of the ordinary."},{"time":351132,"text":"They are just using their bodies"},{"time":353481,"text":"to the best of their capacity."},{"time":355790,"text":"So is it really fair to objectify them"},{"time":359293,"text":"in the way that we do,"},{"time":361016,"text":"to share those images?"},{"time":363118,"text":"People, when they say, \"You're an inspiration,\""},{"time":367641,"text":"they mean it as a compliment."},{"time":370926,"text":"And I know why it happens."},{"time":372292,"text":"It's because of the lie, it's because we've been sold"},{"time":374564,"text":"this lie that disability makes you exceptional."},{"time":378778,"text":"And it honestly doesn't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380612,"text":"And I know what you're thinking."},{"time":381971,"text":"You know, I'm up here bagging out inspiration,"},{"time":384720,"text":"and you're thinking, \"Jeez, Stella,"},{"time":386639,"text":"aren't you inspired sometimes by some things?\""},{"time":390756,"text":"And the thing is, I am."},{"time":392850,"text":"I learn from other disabled people all the time."},{"time":395888,"text":"I'm learning not that I am luckier than them, though."},{"time":400827,"text":"I am learning that it's a genius idea"},{"time":403982,"text":"to use a pair of barbecue tongs"},{"time":405403,"text":"to pick up things that you dropped. (Laughter)"},{"time":411160,"text":"I'm learning that nifty trick where you can charge"},{"time":413681,"text":"your mobile phone battery from your chair battery."},{"time":418266,"text":"Genius."},{"time":419480,"text":"We are learning from each\nothers' strength and endurance,"},{"time":422061,"text":"not against our bodies and our diagnoses,"},{"time":424702,"text":"but against a world that exceptionalizes"},{"time":427506,"text":"and objectifies us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429963,"text":"I really think that this lie that we've been sold"},{"time":432598,"text":"about disability is the greatest injustice."},{"time":436821,"text":"It makes life hard for us."},{"time":440956,"text":"And that quote, \"The only disability in life"},{"time":444829,"text":"is a bad attitude,\""},{"time":446827,"text":"the reason that that's bullshit"},{"time":449954,"text":"is because it's just not true,"},{"time":451575,"text":"because of the social model of disability."},{"time":454237,"text":"No amount of smiling at a flight of stairs"},{"time":458402,"text":"has ever made it turn into a ramp."},{"time":463348,"text":"Never. (Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":469930,"text":"Smiling at a television screen"},{"time":471810,"text":"isn't going to make closed captions appear"},{"time":473641,"text":"for people who are deaf."},{"time":475374,"text":"No amount of standing\nin the middle of a bookshop"},{"time":477836,"text":"and radiating a positive attitude"},{"time":479606,"text":"is going to turn all those books into braille."},{"time":482305,"text":"It's just not going to happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486509,"text":"I really want to live in a world"},{"time":489236,"text":"where disability is not the exception, but the norm."},{"time":492900,"text":"I want to live in a world where a 15-year-old girl"},{"time":495096,"text":"sitting in her bedroom"},{"time":496830,"text":"watching \"Buffy the Vampire Slayer\""},{"time":499007,"text":"isn't referred to as achieving anything"},{"time":501545,"text":"because she's doing it sitting down."},{"time":503811,"text":"I want to live in a world"},{"time":505236,"text":"where we don't have such low expectations"},{"time":508361,"text":"of disabled people"},{"time":509910,"text":"that we are congratulated for getting out of bed"},{"time":512236,"text":"and remembering our own names in the morning."},{"time":515033,"text":"I want to live in a world where\nwe value genuine achievement"},{"time":518454,"text":"for disabled people,"},{"time":520217,"text":"and I want to live in a world"},{"time":521824,"text":"where a kid in year 11 in a Melbourne high school"},{"time":525236,"text":"is not one bit surprised"},{"time":527589,"text":"that his new teacher is a wheelchair user."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530747,"text":"Disability doesn't make you exceptional,"},{"time":533790,"text":"but questioning what you\nthink you know about it does."}]},{"cues":[{"time":537243,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538510,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}